{"thag2.36:0.1":"Theragatha 2.36 ","thag2.36:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.36:0.3":"Catutthavagga ","thag2.36:0.4":"Nitakattheragatha ","thag2.36:1.1":"“Kassa selupamam cittam, ","thag2.36:1.2":"thitam nanupakampati; ","thag2.36:1.3":"Virattam rajaniyesu, ","thag2.36:1.4":"kuppaniye na kuppati; ","thag2.36:1.5":"Yassevam bhavitam cittam, ","thag2.36:1.6":"kuto tam dukkhamessati. ","thag2.36:2.1":"Mama selupamam cittam, ","thag2.36:2.2":"thitam nanupakampati; ","thag2.36:2.3":"Virattam rajaniyesu, ","thag2.36:2.4":"kuppaniye na kuppati; ","thag2.36:2.5":"Mamevam bhavitam cittam, ","thag2.36:2.6":"kuto mam dukkhamessati”ti. ","thag2.36:2.7":"… Nitako thero …. "}